1 cd myProject

2 //authorize the org ( d - default, a - alias)
sfdx force:auth:web:login -d -a myOrg

3 login+password in browser

4 // create project with conf files in the folder
sfdx force:project:create -n myFirstProject

5 // go to new created project folder and run to create the actual scrtach org (s - scratch is default, f - cong file path,  a - alias)
sfdx force:org:create -s -f config/enterprise-scratch-def.json -a MyScratchOrg

6 verify scratch created (list of devhubs and scratch org)
sfdx force:org:list
D - dev hub
U - scratch org

7 // create one more time if after 7 days old expired
sfdx force:org:create -s -f config/enterprise-scratch-def.json -a MyScratchOrg 

8 // push code to scratch org
sfdx force:source:push   

9 // after it push to open browser and see changes online
sfdx force:org:open   // to open browser and see changes online

10
u can setup > lightning app builder > drag custom lwc component > enable and see
